“Series Content Experience the wonders of our world like never before in this epic documentary produced by Jon Favreau and the producers of our planet Earth. Travel back 66 million years when still majestic dinosaurs and extraordinary creatures roamed the earth, water, air.”

Seasons: 1 (2022)

Status: Finished

Creator: Michael Gunton

Channel: Apple TV

Starring: David Attenborough
